        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><strong>No Tax Breaks for Radical Corporate Activism Act</strong></p> <p>This bill disallows a business expense tax deduction for any reimbursement paid by an employer to an employee for travel expenses to obtain an abortion, or for the costs of any gender transition procedure for the employee's minor child.</p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
